---
/** Diagrama flujo app + CTA inferior. */
---
      <section
        data-landing-reveal
        style="--lr-delay: 30ms"
        class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/55 dark:bg-gray-950/45 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800/70 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 backdrop-blur flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-3">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.workflowVizKicker">
              Dentro de la app
            </p>
            <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowVizTitle">De la base al portfolio, y más allá.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl" data-i18n="landing.workflowVizSubtitle">
            Flujo de trabajo real: mapa de habilidades, proyectos con evidencias, salidas públicas y preparación para convocatorias.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-linear-to-br from-white/90 via-white/75 to-indigo-50/30 dark:from-gray-950/75 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-indigo-950/20">
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full min-h-[min(52vh,28rem)]" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="bw" x1="0" x2="1" y1="0" y2="0">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgb(99 102 241)" stop-opacity="0.5" />
                    <stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgb(56 189 248)" stop-opacity="0.4" />
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgb(244 63 94)" stop-opacity="0.45" />
                  </linearGradient>
                  <filter id="bwBlur" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
                    <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="0.55" />
                  </filter>
                </defs>
                <path
                  d="M 18 20 C 30 20, 38 50, 50 50"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.58"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 18 50 C 30 50, 38 50, 50 50"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.68"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 18 80 C 30 80, 38 50, 50 50"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.58"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 50 50 C 62 50, 70 16, 82 16"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.58"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 50 50 C 62 50, 70 38, 82 38"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.58"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 50 50 C 62 50, 70 62, 82 62"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.68"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
                <path
                  d="M 50 50 C 62 50, 70 84, 82 84"
                  stroke="url(#bw)"
                  stroke-width="1.35"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  fill="none"
                  opacity="0.58"
                  filter="url(#bwBlur)"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-4 p-5 items-stretch md:min-h-[22rem]">
              <div class="grid grid-rows-3 gap-3 h-full min-h-[12rem]">
                <div class="inline-flex h-full items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
                  <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 dark:bg-indigo-400/10 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 border border-indigo-500/15 dark:border-indigo-400/15">◎</span>
                  <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                    <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft1Title">Tecnologías</p>
                    <p class="mt-0.5 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft1Hint">mapa de stack</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="inline-flex h-full items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
                  <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500/10 dark:bg-sky-400/10 text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 border border-sky-500/15 dark:border-sky-400/15">◇</span>
                  <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                    <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft2Title">Conceptos</p>
                    <p class="mt-0.5 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft2Hint">progreso por tecnología</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="inline-flex h-full items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
                  <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-500/10 dark:bg-violet-400/10 text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300 border border-violet-500/15 dark:border-violet-400/15">⚙</span>
                  <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                    <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft3Title">Ajustes</p>
                    <p class="mt-0.5 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.workflowLeft3Hint">perfil, privacidad, stack</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:min-w-[9.5rem]">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-200/70 dark:border-indigo-900/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-gray-950/90 px-5 py-5 shadow-md text-center ring-1 ring-indigo-500/10 dark:ring-indigo-400/10">
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowCenterLabel">SkillAtlas</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.workflowCenterHint">tu espacio de trabajo</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="grid grid-rows-4 gap-2.5 h-full min-h-[16rem]">
                <div class="inline-flex h-full min-h-0 items-center rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-2.5 shadow-sm justify-between gap-2">
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight1Title">Proyectos</p>
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight1Hint">evidencias</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inline-flex h-full min-h-0 items-center rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-2.5 shadow-sm justify-between gap-2">
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight2Title">Portfolio</p>
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight2Hint">enlace público</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inline-flex h-full min-h-0 items-center rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/75 px-4 py-2.5 shadow-sm justify-between gap-2">
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight3Title">CV</p>
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 shrink-0" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight3Hint">preview · PDF</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inline-flex h-full min-h-0 items-center rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200/80 dark:border-emerald-900/45 bg-emerald-50/50 dark:bg-emerald-950/25 px-4 py-2.5 shadow-sm justify-between gap-2">
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900 dark:text-emerald-100" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight4Title">Preparación</p>
                  <span class="text-xs text-emerald-800/90 dark:text-emerald-200/90 shrink-0" data-i18n="landing.workflowRight4Hint">convocatorias</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200/70 dark:border-emerald-900/40 bg-linear-to-r from-emerald-50/80 via-white/80 to-sky-50/60 dark:from-emerald-950/30 dark:via-gray-950/50 dark:to-sky-950/20 p-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-1 min-w-0">
              <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300" data-i18n="landing.prepTeaserKicker">
                Próxima pieza
              </p>
              <p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.prepTeaserTitle">
                Proyectos de estudio y temario (tipo NotebookLM, a tu manera)
              </p>
              <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.prepTeaserBody">
                Para preparar oposiciones o exámenes técnicos: temario, seguimiento y material enlazado — sin sustituir a NotebookLM; integración razonable por enlaces y exportaciones.
              </p>
            </div>
            <a
              href="/prep"
              class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-600 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-emerald-800 dark:hover:bg-emerald-500 no-underline"
            >
              <span data-i18n="landing.prepTeaserCta">Qué estamos preparando</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section
        data-landing-reveal
        style="--lr-delay: 20ms"
        class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-linear-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900 px-8 py-10 text-center shadow-lg"
      >
        <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="landing.ctaBottomTitle">¿Te cuadra el ritmo?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 mb-0 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.ctaBottomBody">
          Pide acceso, mira precios u holdea la demo. Vamos sin prisas, con buen criterio.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="/request-access"
            data-landing-request-access
            class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 no-underline"
          >
            <span data-i18n="landing.ctaBottomPrimary">Solicitar acceso</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/pricing"
            class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/25 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 no-underline"
          >
            <span data-i18n="landing.ctaBottomPricing">Ver precios</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/demo"
            data-landing-demo
            class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/25 bg-white/5 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 no-underline"
          >
            <span data-i18n="landing.ctaBottomDemo">Demo</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>